---
<div class="bg-brand-blue-darker text-white rounded-2xl p-7 md:p-10">
  <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] opacity-70 font-bold mb-3 text-brand-red-soft">CCI / FasCard app</p>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">Start your laundry<br/>from your phone.</h2>
  <p class="opacity-80 mb-6 max-w-md leading-relaxed">Free app from Card Concepts Inc. See open machines, start a cycle by scanning the code, and get a push notification when it's done.</p>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
    <a href={links.ios} class="bg-white text-brand-blue-darker font-bold text-sm px-6 py-3 rounded-full inline-flex items-center gap-2">
